{"tid":1560243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開始支爆，大家繼續加油！","createTime":"2019-09-11T06:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:54:11.000Z","uid":301585,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c183a757641af1bf71a44f14550b3bc62e0970f5","tid":1560243,"uid":301585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"國務院關稅稅則委員會公布，第一批對美國加徵關稅商品第一次排除清單，自本月17日起實施。<br />\n<br />\n其中，清單一所列的商品，包括有潤滑油、部分飼料等12類商品，自本月17日至明年9月16日，不再加徵中方為反制美國301條款所加徵的關稅，對已經加徵的關稅稅款予以退還，相關進口企業應自排除清單公布之日起的6個月內，按規定向海關申請辦理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，清單二所列的飼料及潤滑油等商品，在本月17日起的一年內，亦不再加徵中方為反制美國所加徵的關稅，已加徵的關稅稅款不予退還。下一步，國務院關稅稅則委員會將繼續開展對美國加徵關稅商品排除工作，適時公佈後續批次排除清單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479997-20190911.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479997-20190911.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=9c9b1f12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479997-20190911.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b6767da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479997-20190911.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n要穩定豬價，養豬戶之前比你跣過唔肯養翻，依家要死死氣氣取消飼料關稅<br />\n證明大陸係貿易戰面前不堪一擊，我地要繼續加油，繼續捱落去<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"93575a278d29f1b5341194f48ff7dd519ceff3e9","tid":1560243,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:35:21.000Z","msg":"推！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請即參與：#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span></span><br />\n已有手足推緊hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">本地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n1. 將警